Class PokemonSendableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.ac.ulb.infof307.g01.common.model.PokemonSendableModel

  • public class PokemonSendableModel
extends Object
    Represents a pokemon. A pokemon has a name, two types and a corresponding image. The sendable keyword indicates the object can be serialized and sent over the network
